Hello Team, My Current ad account threshold is $10 which is hampering my account transactions could please Increase it to least $50 to $100 or more if Possible also I don't have direct POC for My ad account it would be very great if I could have someone from your team, these are only things that restricting me to ad spend

Thanks for reaching out! Currently, dedicated account management is reserved for advertisers who meet a daily spend threshold of $1,000 or more. If you’re not at that level yet, our self-serve platform has everything you need to launch and optimize your campaigns successfully. For increasing your ad account threshold, please ensure that your account completes and passes business verification and accumulates over $5,000 in spend. Once these conditions are met, you can establish a relationship with an Account Manager who can assist further. If you have any questions or need help getting started, feel free to reach out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.
I used to work with one of your POC right now If you could connect me with her that would also be great.

I understand you're looking to reconnect with a previous point of contact. Unfortunately, I don't have access to specific personnel assignments or contact details. If you meet the daily spend threshold of $1,000 or more, you can request dedicated account management by providing a media plan, billing statement, or screenshot showing your ad spend. For further assistance, please reach out to our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com.
